{"tid":211743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"『用肉體交租』業主免租，利誘租客做私家炮友","createTime":"2017-04-22T00:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-22T09:48:41.000Z","uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"50956e3c8129fc2b1a567ec1ec427006061e9925","tid":211743,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T00:01:31.000Z","msg":"幾時香港會興起？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國樓價高企一室難求，記者發現有業主利用樓價及租金齊升局面，提出以性服務代替交租，業主更在廣告上徵求淫蕩室友，有的更留下露骨形容，甚至當上扯皮條為租戶拉客......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國廣播公司調查後發現不少提出「以身體交租」的網上廣告<span style=\"color: red;\">針對年輕人</span>，..........布萊頓一名業主更針對年輕男性落廣告。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者發現提出以性換租的業主都很清楚要如何安排，一名倫敦業主便要求「蕩女孩」搬進來，<span style=\"color: red;\">有的更設下年齡限制甚至要求租戶先傳照片</span>，一人說：「我想要一星期一次，類似這樣的，只要有性我便高興。」"},{"pid":"2cf7d4edfe549e3022e5b2983480a1efcf1a7d52","tid":211743,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T00:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170421/large/1492757625_c399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170421%2Flarge%2F1492757625_c399.jpg&h=512f1680&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06dec14670a76c73a671391b0344b3e449392519","tid":211743,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T00:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170421/large/1492757627_6213.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170421%2Flarge%2F1492757627_6213.jpg&h=fd400743&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7aeeb8cc932297a9c00a7db1d5e18c0fdf555505","tid":211743,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T00:03:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170421/large/1492757628_dbe5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic